== Russian ==

=== Verb ===
'''использо́вывать''' (ispol'zóvyvat') (''[[impf.]], ''transitive''), same as [[использовать]]

# incorrect imperfective form of [[использовать]] ([[использовать]] is simultaneously imperfective and perfective verb), was widespread during 1920s in Russia

